{
  "stem": "13911.7",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then there was a refugee camp in-- in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we-- and there were a lot of Jews there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we-- because like in the-- in the-- it was in-- in Berlin, near Berlin.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we went to that refugee camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, I always remembered.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh my god.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I forgot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Unless I can-- I can't put it in later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, I-- this, I just forgot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went there, stayed a-- not too long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From there, we went to-- they thought-- I don't know, wherever they thought-- first of all, we were-- we liked to roam around.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we were going from camp to-- especially my husband.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a very caring, family person, kind of.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Although he was young, but looking for a relatives.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My brother-in-law, he was younger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So where are you going?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, go look.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Go find a-- a pin in an ocean.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was going for-- so we were going from camp to camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we went-- we heard there is another camp, Camp [NON-ENGLISH] in Eschwege Hessen, was the name of the place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to that camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were quite a few Jews, you know, from all over Poland, or wherever, not even Poland, in that camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And life was already-- it was, of course, very primitive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We lived in a-- like, in a barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- we didn't-- we have-- the floors were cement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not-- Really lived-- no, I can't even call it primitive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But just enough to survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, they were barracks for the armies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The [GERMAN] were stationed there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were like military barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You-- you know, this is another thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I'm trying to remember one meal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
